<treatmentCitation author="Komiya, Z." box="[331,527,1510,1534]" page="220" pageId="1" pageNumber="376" year="2002">
<bibRefCitation author="Komiya, Z." box="[331,527,1510,1534]" pageId="1" pageNumber="376" pagination="219 - 234" refId="ref5366" refString="Komiya, Z. (2002) A Synopsis of the Prionine Cerambycid of the Genus Megobaralipton, New Status (Coleoptera, Cerambycidae, Prioninae). (Revisional Studies of the Genus Megopis sensu Lameere, 1909 - 1). Elytra, 30 (1), 219 - 234., 23 figs." type="journal article" year="2002">Komiya, 2002: 220</bibRefCitation>
