<treatmentCitation author="Komiya, Z. &amp; Drumont, A." box="[787,1109,1510,1534]" page="188" pageId="1" pageNumber="376" year="2014">
<bibRefCitation author="Komiya, Z. &amp; Drumont, A." box="[787,1109,1510,1534]" pageId="1" pageNumber="376" pagination="187 - 199" refId="ref5526" refString="Komiya, Z. &amp; Drumont, A. (2014) Supplement to the Genus Megobaralipton (Coleoptera, Cerambycidae, Prioninae) (Revisional Studies of the Genus Megopis sensu Lameere, 1909 - 13). Elytra, (New Series), 4 (2), 187 - 199, 25 figs." type="journal article" year="2014">Komiya &amp; Drumont, 2014: 188</bibRefCitation>
